'''硫氰酸铷'''是一种[[无机化合物|无机化合物]]，化学式为RbSCN，它可由[[硫氰酸|硫氰酸]]和[[碳酸铷|碳酸铷]]反应制得。它在195 °C熔化，在空气中加热至500~600 °C按下式分解：<ref>{{cite journal|last1=Ptaszyński|first1=B.|last2=Skiba|first2=E.|last3=Krystek|first3=J.|title=Thermal decomposition of alkali metal, copper(I) and silver(I) thiocyanates|journal=Thermochimica Acta|volume=319|issue=1-2|year=1998|pages=75–85|issn=00406031|doi=10.1016/S0040-6031(98)00391-8}}</ref>

: 2 RbSCN + 5 O<sub>2</sub> → Rb<sub>2</sub>SO<sub>4</sub> + SO<sub>2</sub> + 2 CO<sub>2</sub> + N<sub>2</sub>

它和四氢噻吩氯化亚金在[[乙腈|乙腈]]中反应，得到Rb[Au(SCN)<sub>2</sub>]。<ref>{{cite journal|last1=Coker|first1=Nathan L.|last2=Krause Bauer|first2=Jeanette A.|last3=Elder|first3=R. C.|title=Emission Energy Correlates with Inverse of Gold−Gold Distance for Various [Au(SCN)<sub>2</sub>]<sup>−</sup> Salts|journal=Journal of the American Chemical Society|volume=126|issue=1|year=2004|pages=12–13|issn=0002-7863|doi=10.1021/ja037012f}}</ref>它和[[草酸铷|草酸铷]]与[[硒酸铀酰|硒酸铀酰]]反应，得到单斜晶系的Rb[UO<sub>2</sub>(C<sub>2</sub>O<sub>4</sub>)(NCS)]·{{frac|2}}H<sub>2</sub>O晶体。<ref>Medrish, I. V.; Peresypkina, E. V.; Virovets, A. V.; Serezhkina, L. B. Synthesis and structure of M[UO<sub>2</sub>(C<sub>2</sub>O<sub>4</sub>)​(NCS)​]​·0.5H<sub>2</sub>O (M = Rb or Cs). ''Zhurnal Neorganicheskoi Khimii'', 2008. 53 (7): 1121-1126. ISSN: 0044-457X.</ref>

